      • getDistinctTrajectoryIDs

        public java.lang.String getDistinctTrajectoryIDs(java.lang.String delimiter)
        Returns a trajectory ID /** Returns distinct trajectory IDs separated by delimiter. i.e., if there is only one distinct trajectory Id in the the arraylist of trajectory IDs, else returns the distinct trajIDs separated by delimiter. There is an arraylist of trajectory ids in the first place to allow for multiple trajectory entries (with same or difference trajectory IDs) to be merged.
        Parameters:
        delimiter -
        Returns:
